ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_FISTS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Power Fists</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pięści mocy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_FISTS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A melee punching attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ciosy pięściami zdawane w walce wręcz.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HIGH_MORALE_AURA</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">High Morale Aura</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aura wysokiego morale</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HIGH_MORALE_AURA</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit disperses mood-enhancer pheromones, making adjacent friendly Biological or Cyborg units gain {HighMorale}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka rozsiewa poprawiające nastrój feromony, dzięki czemu sąsiadujące z nią przyjazne jednostki organiczne i cyborgi uzyskują {HighMorale}.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_DISTRACTING_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Distracting Pheromones</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Feromony rozpraszające</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_DISTRACTING_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Disperse a cloud of artificial pheromones that has a {DistractingChance} strength chance to apply [abilityred]Distracted[/abilityred] to non-Mindless Biological or Cyborg units, making their attacks {ChanceFumble} more likely to Fumble, for {Duration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rozpyla chmurę sztucznych feromonów, które mają szansę ({DistractingChance} siły) na spowodowanie [abilityred]rozproszenia[/abilityred] niebezmózgich jednostek organicznych i cyborgów. Efekt ten zwiększa o {ChanceFumble} prawdopodobieństwo, że jednostki te spudłują.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_LOVE_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Love Pheromones</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Feromony miłosne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_LOVE_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Target Biological or Cyborg unit must resist a {LoveChance} strength chance to become [abilityred]Mind Controlled[/abilityred] until the end of combat.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wskazana jednostka organiczna lub cyborg musi odeprzeć [abilityred]kontrolę umysłu[/abilityred] (szansa równa {LoveChance} siły na to, że jednostka będzie kontrolowana do końca bitwy).</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_DISTRACTING_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Distracted</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rozproszenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISPERSE_DISTRACTING_PHEROMONES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UNIT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit has a {Fumblechance} chance for its attacks to Fumble.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka ma {Fumblechance} szans na spudłowanie.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Added "chance"</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, any inserted strings - anything of the form {text} - is replaced by an integer value for the thing described in the brackets. If the {text} is not followed by a unit - e.g. shields, hitpoints - the icon for the unit is inserted together with the integer. The same holds for symbols - e.g. '+', '%' - which are occasionally inserted together with the integer.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">For references to game terminology and in-world references, please check the glossary delivered as part of the documentation.</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><Panes><Pane><Number>3</Number><ActiveRow>26</ActiveRow><ActiveCol>2</ActiveCol></Pane></Panes><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>